<section xml:id="xdiff.installation" xmlns="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink">
 &reftitle.install;
 <para>
  xdiff eklentisi PECL
  <link xlink:href="&url.pecl.package;xdiff">&url.pecl.package;xdiff</link>
  adresinden edinilebilir.
 </para>
 <para>
  *nix benzeri işletim sisteminizde <link xlink:href="&url.php.pear;">
  PEAR</link> kuruluysa xdiff eklentisini şu komutla kurabilirsiniz:
  <command>pear -v install xdiff</command>.
 </para>
 <para>
  xdiff'in tar.gz paketini indirip kurulumu kendiniz de yapabilirsiniz:
  <example>
   <title>- xdiff eklentisini elle kurmak</title>
   <programlisting role="shell">
<![CDATA[
gunzip xdiff-xxx.tgz
tar -xvf xdiff-xxx.tar
cd xdiff-xxx
phpize
./configure && make && make install
]]>
   </programlisting>
  </example>
 </para>
</section>

